# GestorBar

**Sistema POS para gestão de bares e restaurantes**

[![Versão](https://img.shields.io/badge/versão-2.6.4-blue?style=flat-square)](https://github.com/Joaovdsmaranhao/GestorBar-releases/releases)
[![Plataforma](https://img.shields.io/badge/plataforma-Windows-0078D6?style=flat-square&logo=windows)](https://github.com/Joaovdsmaranhao/GestorBar-releases/releases)
